      "body" : "To be clear, there is no \"switch\": Python3 is installed by default. Python2 is installed optionally. These have co-existed for quite a while, and can still happily coexist, but a lot of people think Python2's EOL is starting to approach. Distributions dropping Python 2 from the default (minimal) install is a clear omen to that.\r\n",
